data.description: This Beauty is Back on the Market, with a price reduction! Come see the brand new carpet!! You'll Love the mountain views and starlit nights in this immaculately well-kept and maintained Brick Multi-level. Enjoy larger than most living, family, and bedroom areas. Light and bright throughout with Oversized Bay window and French doors. Laminate wood floors and contrasting wood trim & door casings, along with all neutral paint, reflect the quality of construction and is the perfect canvas for you to add your own touches. Master suite boasts separate vanity area, recently re-tiled shower, and 2 closets with organizers as do all the bedrooms. As a bonus, there's a kitchenette in the lower level, where you can watch movies or use as a mother-in-law suite. Take peace of mind that the furnace, central air, water heater, driveway, and roof have all been replaced in the last 5 yrs or so. This one owner home is just waiting for you! Easy to show! Make an offer today!
